{"tid":2041792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱西伯格：希望香港第時仲有fb用","createTime":"2020-05-29T12:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T12:38:50.000Z","uid":228995,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4db7f4223c3bf57ffddeca71ef3b9cf236c8e238","tid":2041792,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"美國係咪要制裁香港剩係畀香港人用Wechat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還是北京準備加防火牆<br />\n<br />\nFacebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg told &quot;The Daily Briefing&quot; Thursday that he hopes Facebook will &quot;find a way&quot; to keep offering its services in Hong Kong after Secretary of State Mike Pompeo declared this week that the city was &quot;no longer autonomous&quot; from China.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;People across Hong Kong really love our services,&quot; Zuckerberg told host Dana Perino, noting that residents particularly appreciate the &quot;encrypted&quot; nature of Facebook's WhatsApp messaging service. &quot;People use Facebook in order to stay in touch with their friends and family around the whole world, and I certainly hope that we'll find a way to keep offering the services over the long term.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nZuckerberg explained that China and North Korea are the two major countries where Facebook either does not or cannot offer their services due to what he called &quot;pretty oppressive policies.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The reality here,&quot; he added &quot;... is that China has just approached the Internet very differently from the U.S. and even Europe and most other places.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe United Kingdom ceded Hong Kong to China in 1997 under the terms of a 1984 agreement which guaranteed that the former British colony would retain a &quot;high degree of autonomy,&quot; a principle known as &quot;One Country, Two Systems.&quot;"},{"pid":"2bb52fdcd1fd7c7b2cf948da08dbe01cb3ca6258","tid":2041792,"uid":224657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母豬閪伯格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd9b992df18e8041dacedfd7180ed67e0fc90c4","tid":2041792,"uid":154486,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"講左<br />\n香港人好快冇得用國際版FB﹐IG, WTSAPP<br />\n之前講過乜野hide一hide"},{"pid":"4b1c24a140da8e945123fc2fbb3e1de68fdbe0b9","tid":2041792,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"而家先黎講，炒撚晒班支那人外判moderator先啦，仲要cut鳩埋save hk呀on9"},{"pid":"938879bc0f5709565aa52d92c717f3117c01c110","tid":2041792,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"love your service? 咪撚講笑啦"},{"pid":"7c1f4f35c5b0f245f83c0aa9c87e33e4f750f1a3","tid":2041792,"uid":27700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"Find a way 淨返藍絲 同 小粉紅 post 而家都做緊"},{"pid":"03aa3d39dca9d5e917b0fd1c41ae439e57f4fdd1","tid":2041792,"uid":297949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48d6aacda5da81d05dedd4ddcc18d18f2873f1e","tid":2041792,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a5dab21673d6be54f547a25541277b2ef8fe8a5","tid":2041792,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"一定有 fb奶共奶到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"25f3a45ae1a8749af817a6330af39d1bfe1796cb","tid":2041792,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi